          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The density of the T-Ti target used was 2.18",
                "mg/cm2, the average energy and the intensity of the",
                "incident deuterium beam were 134 keV and about 230 uA,",
                "the neutron yield was about 2.0E11 n/s."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A certain mass of high-purity uranium nitrate",
                " (UO2(NO3)2) powder was pressed into the mold. The",
                "diameter of the mold was 12 mm, and the thickness was",
                "about 1 mm. Three sample targets were placed at",
                "different angles (0, 45, 90 deg relative to the",
                "incident direction of the deuterium beam)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A high sensitivity HPGe detector with a low",
                "background lead chamber. The HPGe detector was",
                "connected to a general-purpose spectrometer",
                "amplifier (572A from ORTEC) with a shaping time of 1",
                "us. The energy and efficiency calibration of",
                "HPGe-gamma spectrometers had been carried out",
                "carefully using 60Co, 137Cs, 152Eu and 241Am standard",
                "sources. The detector had an absolute efficiency of",
                "0.504% at 1.173 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The irradiation time is about 7000 s, the",
                "cooling time is about 300 s, and a about 5000 s",
                "period was arranged for the measurement."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
                "reaction": {
                  "code": "13-AL-27(N,A)11-NA-24,,SIG",
